   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Thoth 13. Brought for the villagers of Karanis, through Isak, son of Ision, for the 16th indiction, one-hundred and twenty litrai of chaff, 120 litrai. (2nd hand) I, Diatimos(?), have signed.</ab>
